---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Use Case: Validate Stored Time">
  <article class="panel">
    <h1>Validate a stored time snapshot</h1>
    <p>
      Use <code>GET /secnow</code> to capture signed snapshots, then later submit the exact payload to
      <code>POST /validate</code> to confirm it was not tampered.
    </p>
    <h2>Flow</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Capture signed payload from <code>/secnow</code>.</li>
      <li>Persist <code>format</code>, <code>timestamp</code>, <code>signature</code>, and <code>token</code>.</li>
      <li>Send payload to <code>/validate</code> before trusting stored values.</li>
    </ol>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
